0. INTRODUCTION
===============

Ruby/Cares is a C extension for the c-ares[1] library. It provides an
asynchronous DNS resolver to be used with ruby scripts.


1. REQUIREMENTS
===============

Ruby/Cares requires c-ares to be installed. It was developed and tested
using Ruby 1.8.4.


2. INSTALLATION
===============

To install manually:

$ ruby extconf.rb
$ make
# make install

To install from rubygems:

# gem install ruby-cares


